Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.16,0:00:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦开始的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.30,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炫目的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.93,0:00:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪感觉冰凉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.60,0:00:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小野花的香味很温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.34,0:00:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外还有小孩子在哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.38,0:00:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经想不起当时的哭声了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.74,0:00:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间的黄昏的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.82,0:01:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行着一段永远的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.83,0:01:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的指尖继续探索着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.17,0:01:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎片发出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.31,0:01:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧的抱住胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.65,0:01:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻找遗失的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.79,0:01:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用双手的掌心确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.16,0:01:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在新的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.54,0:01:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间开始流动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.96,0:02:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就来解决这长年的怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.73,0:02:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.34,0:02:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我不记得有与人结怨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.71,0:02:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,废话少说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.35,0:02:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要躲开嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.55,0:02:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.29,0:02:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「唯一的小小的回忆」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.54,0:02:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.01,0:03:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.78,0:03:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.85,0:03:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.68,0:03:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.99,0:03:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜\N好过份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道我成了坏人了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.33,0:03:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.53,0:03:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨 你怎么会在这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来买东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.26,0:03:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.84,0:03:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身上都弄脏了\N佑一也来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.14,0:03:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能这样丢下她不管吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.55,0:03:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去铺床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.19,0:03:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想问这个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.68,0:04:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是佑一不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我可是被害人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.35,0:04:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她自己对我打过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你太迟钝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.63,0:04:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是你不自觉的\N给别人带来麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.64,0:04:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没见过她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.91,0:04:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.21,0:04:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别欺负她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.98,0:04:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等她醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.42,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候再问清楚也不迟吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.93,0:05:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管清不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.67,0:05:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也不记得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.84,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是只有我自己忘了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小时候的回忆我都记不起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.77,0:05:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.44,0:05:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有吃的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.59,0:06:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了会吵到邻居的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为她在翻冰箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.37,0:06:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.91,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上来煮宵夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宵夜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.35,0:06:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一也来吃吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.06,0:06:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好困啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,困了可以去睡觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.33,0:06:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血型？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的艺人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.77,0:06:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泽渡真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只记得这个嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.32,0:07:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其它的都记不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.38,0:07:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会丧失记忆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要找借口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说跟我有仇吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.89,0:07:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你丧失记忆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还记得有仇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么一看到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就有一把无名火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.15,0:07:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样穷追不舍的对她太可怜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.69,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.12,0:07:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们应该也不相信她说的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.13,0:07:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些是她包包里的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.33,0:07:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放了好多东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以乱动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了确认她的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.34,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有这些吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.25,0:08:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.98,0:08:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管她是不是丧失记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.78,0:08:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来似乎真有隐情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.09,0:08:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何朋友家人的线索吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来似乎真有原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.85,0:08:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.65,0:08:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个今天都好早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天早起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.99,0:08:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是根本没睡吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们做了什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.63,0:08:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.17,0:09:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们该不会是\N黏在一起开夜车吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.47,0:09:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.64,0:09:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸好红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.69,0:09:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以逃课哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.26,0:09:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还说别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身体好一点了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像还得继续请假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.37,0:09:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你又是怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.91,0:09:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像脸色不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.18,0:09:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丧失记忆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.88,0:09:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是骗人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.62,0:09:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是离家出走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想回去也不能回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后骗取大人的同情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闯荡江湖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.43,0:10:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个大坏蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.36,0:10:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高兴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是很酷吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丧失记忆 好像连续剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.14,0:10:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.07,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现实跟连续剧是不一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我只顾着自己说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.89,0:10:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.50,0:10:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不要在外面闲晃比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.43,0:10:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不乖一点的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.73,0:10:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会好的病都好不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.68,0:10:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诗织 下次见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是能像她一样讨人喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.15,0:11:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就不会那么讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.69,0:11:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是问题不只是这种程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.99,0:11:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家看这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.56,0:11:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里会考 要好好记下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.70,0:11:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“蠢蛋 笨蛋”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相泽 怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.31,0:11:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么喜欢考试吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.21,0:11:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.38,0:11:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“笨蛋”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.49,0:11:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管有什么深仇大恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不需要做到这种地步吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.29,0:11:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.43,0:11:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为这样就没事了\N真是大错特错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.50,0:11:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来翻开课本的213页
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.31,0:12:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的笔记本等一下借你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.64,0:12:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.85,0:12:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你干的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.48,0:12:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还把我的自动铅笔拆开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,橡皮擦弄成碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.79,0:12:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别装傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.12,0:12:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.09,0:12:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我之前也干过\N碰过这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.76,0:12:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不要偷拿别人的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.43,0:12:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的钱包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.97,0:12:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放在制服的口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.60,0:13:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天在学校要吃饭时\N却不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你说说看是谁拿的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.61,0:13:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 真的不知道嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的漫画吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是进了你的房间没错\N但是钱包我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.32,0:13:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我会相信你吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.07,0:13:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该出去的是你吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.44,0:13:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.24,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.17,0:13:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 我有事情麻烦你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以来一下吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思要你陪我出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的帮了我很大的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.22,0:13:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外还有她的事情吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情变得麻烦了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.83,0:14:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也想要相信她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.77,0:14:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在做什么都没用了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.07,0:14:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种大骗子 还是报警…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又撞到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.62,0:14:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.23,0:14:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你讨厌我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有精神的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.81,0:14:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.04,0:14:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我寄住的亲戚家的秋子阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.62,0:14:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.98,0:14:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我是月宫亚由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.62,0:14:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月宫亚由…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.36,0:14:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.89,0:15:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸上有什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有两个眼睛一个鼻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.60,0:15:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一果然讨厌我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.17,0:15:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌我了…\N我根本没有这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.74,0:15:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 是我太多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.21,0:15:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.59,0:15:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.99,0:15:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又吃了就跑了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.39,0:15:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正要去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.23,0:15:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在找东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.63,0:15:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我掉了东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.47,0:15:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱包吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 更重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我掉的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.08,0:15:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了？\N是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.69,0:16:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是很重要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该要快点找到才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.79,0:16:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却想不起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.77,0:16:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候冷静下来反而可以找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.34,0:16:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再找找看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.28,0:16:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道要找的是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就免谈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油 我支持你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.35,0:16:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那下次见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.79,0:16:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是个好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.06,0:16:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我还没有介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.54,0:16:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是水濑名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我名雪就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.77,0:16:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.44,0:16:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的表哥佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是骗人小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.92,0:17:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.88,0:17:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是偷钱包小姐呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那种怪名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.26,0:17:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是泽渡真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有证据吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.40,0:17:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能证明你真的叫做泽渡真琴吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.61,0:17:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要我叫你的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.57,0:17:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就老实承认偷了钱包\N并且道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.48,0:17:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.98,0:17:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你说钱包？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.35,0:17:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她偷了我的钱包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.12,0:17:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 那是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.50,0:17:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天抱她去房间时掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你捡起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.21,0:18:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算待会拿给你却忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.01,0:18:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.59,0:18:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不对 但是你也不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.73,0:18:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是你先来找上我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不会发生这些事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.63,0:18:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且为什么找上我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.40,0:18:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会跟你结下梁子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认错人了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.21,0:18:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且越说我越确定是你没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我忘了很多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.09,0:18:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是找到你的时候\N我想起了一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.33,0:18:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我跟你有仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.33,0:19:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,线索就是你是佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.67,0:19:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,线索？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.54,0:19:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟佑一在一起\N说不定可以恢复记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.41,0:19:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她恢复记忆之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.08,0:19:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就先留在我们家吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.35,0:19:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.75,0:19:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.99,0:19:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们吃东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.66,0:19:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是真琴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.23,0:19:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的名字是泽渡真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.18,0:19:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.03,0:20:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 笔记本还我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笔记本？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.43,0:20:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的笔记本借你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笔记本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.04,0:20:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.84,0:20:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 明天去学校再还你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.08,0:20:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的笔记本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.91,0:20:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.08,0:20:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就去学校拿回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.72,0:20:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学校应该关门了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有值班老师吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.62,0:20:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面很冷哦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.13,0:20:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.33,0:20:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要呼吸外面的空气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.97,0:20:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为愚蠢的我\N误以为她是小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.11,0:20:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我都要喘不过气来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.74,0:21:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.07,0:21:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戏剧社在练习吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.74,0:21:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.04,0:21:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.21,0:22:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.55,0:22:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是打击恶魔之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.40,0:22:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从随风飘流的云朵之间\N窥视到晴空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.55,0:22:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连熟悉的街道也闪闪发光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.73,0:22:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前奔跑的小小的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.06,0:22:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时的两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.07,0:23:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用天真来盖过溢出的疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.88,0:23:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间静悄悄的流动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.62,0:23:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹拂着温柔的风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.03,0:23:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为冻僵的思念也会化做笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.38,0:23:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在晚上的学校遇到的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与白天印象完全不同的面貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.95,0:23:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夺走了我的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.49,0:23:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanon第4话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.52,0:23:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜里
